Opening Line

“I’m living my dreams. Not above my means.”

No shade, just facts! Ego and fear can’t bog down your boho spirit. As the most positive soul in the sisterhood, you radiate a warm exuberance that burns off any gloomy overcast. Challenges along your path illuminated who you are and why you’re here. You bare your soul, hide nothing, and share everything. From the pit of your stomach and bottom of your heart, you are brimming over with bright confidence and joy. Abundance flows through your playful innocence and purity of heart. Invigorated with a zeal and zest for the future, you know everything will work out-- it always does. So sit back, blow a joint, and rest at ease. Life is good and you are grateful!

Signature

Eva moves in positivity. Sunlight is not selective, so love can spread to any situation:
